Package net.sf.jdivelog.ci.ostc

Interface Summary
OSTCValue Marker interface for OSTC Values.
 

Class Summary
AbstractOSTCProtocol Base Class for all OSTC Protocol Drivers.
ColorValue 8-bit Value for Custom Function
EightBitCustomFunction 8-bit Value for Custom Function
Feature Describes a feature of the OSTC divecomputer.
FifteenBitCustomFunction 15-bit Value for Custom Function
FourBitCustomFunction 8-bit Value for Custom Function
OSTCMix Mix for set on divecomputer
OSTCProtocol070511 Protocol for the first version of the OSTC
OSTCProtocol080115 Same Protocol as 1.0 Versions, but it has a function to reset DecoInformation and a function to read only EEPROM values rather than the whole profile memory.
OSTCProtocol080121 Protocol for the first version of the OSTC
OSTCProtocol080321 OSTC Protocol for Firmware 1.9 and newer.
OSTCProtocol081130 OSTC Protocol for Firmware > 1.17
OSTCProtocol100801 OSTC Protocol for Firmware > 1.17
OSTCProtocol100801Mk2 OSTC Protocol for Firmware > 1.17
OSTCProtocol110119Mk2 OSTC Protocol for Fimware >=1.80
ParseUtil Some universal OSTC Profile Parsing Routines.
Profiles  
ProgrammableMix Mix for set on divecomputer
RadioButtonValue Selection Value
ReadonlyInteger Type for Integer Values which can not be modified.
TextValue Text Field on OSTC
 

Exception Summary
UnknownFeatureException Exception when a feature does not exist on a specific driver.
